Zenbudget

intro:
a simple test to demostrate some basic ruby on rails and some jquery stuff.
Users have a simple way to track expenses and income on a single page.

technology:

css
- 960px.
- simple generic layout.

jquery
- basic jquery used for replace elements on a page.
- sparklines. for simple charts. 

rails
- devise. authorization.
- cancan. authencation.
- kamini. for pagination.
